title: Emoticons Color Palette
description: Pre-configured color palettes optimized for emotes, charts, and branded experiences. Ideal for visual design and campaign planning.
fullDescription: Pre-configured color palettes optimized for emotes, charts, and branded experiences. Ideal for visual design, campaign planning, or email styling.
